data.description: SELLER READY FOR THEIR NEXT BIG ADVENTURE! Discover the essence of this Barndominium on 1.899 acres has 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, 1 half bath with open floor plan. Kitchen and dining open to the living room for warm gathering area. Kitchen has beautiful granite countertops with island that has bar area for enjoying breakfast or visiting while hosting dinners. Master bedroom is spacious with large walk-in closet located in the bathroom and dual vanities in bathroom. Granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms. Bedrooms have plenty of room for large beds and more. All bedrooms are carpeted. 2 car carport. Garden space with upgraded soil content for growing your favorite veggies. 30 amp hook up available for RV and water from home accessible for RV. 1 acre fenced for livestock and has shelter for small goats. Great area for your dream farmette or to raise FFA or 4H projects. 2 storage buildings are on the property. Covered porches allow to sit and enjoy. Current loan is assumable!
